FBIS3-44475 "drchi002_n_94019" FBIS-CHI-94-002 Document Type:Daily Report 4 Jan 1994 Economic & Agricultural First Law Office Specializing in Tourism Opened OW3012061793 Beijing XINHUA in English 0059 GMT 30 Dec 93 OW3012061793 Beijing XINHUA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Nanjing, December 30 (XINHUA) -- China's first law office to specialize in cases concerning tourism recently opened business in Nanjing, the capital of east China's Jiangsu Province. The Jinling Law Firm offers services ranging from international tourism, foreign trade and economic cooperation to intellectual property rights. With headquarters in Nanjing, it has set up agencies in the United States, Japan and Hong Kong. The office aims at clients who are either domestic or overseas tourist agencies, or foreign tourists, investors and businessmen.
